    "Only the first 5, 000 images of the cylinder dataset were considered for GAN training.",
    "Finally, all generative networks were built and trained with PyTorch [122].",
    "A summary and comparison of the relevant training parameters, such as learning rate or effective batch size, of the three generative models investigated can be found in table 1.",
